ike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T06:28:26.000Z","msg":"一百蚊就唔得喇 四五千都有得搞搞佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你先去買兩張廣州直通車飛，就400蚊，再去信和買1000蚊咸碟，同佢講大量買打個折，應該買到50隻以上，要買鬼妹同日本妹的，唔好買其他，理由下面再講。<br />\n<br />\n坐到上廣州你手上仲有100蚊，去買包雲煙5蚊，然後係車站旁邊睇下邊個蛇頭鼠眼，打個眼色比佢佢就知你想唱假人仔，90蚊唱500蚊番黎，同佢講要唱散唔要100蚊紙。唱完拎包煙出黎問佢食唔食，佢見你幫襯佢就有計傾，你打蛇隨棍上問下邊到賣咸碟好。<br />\n<br />\n將淨低果5蚊打散，用1蚊搭巴士入城，搵佢講既地方。然後搵間士多買罐可樂，比唱番黎既假50蚊佢，找番47蚊真人仔，袋好準備最後用。<br />\n<br />\n等到日落你就開始擺地攤，乜都唔洗，只要擺一塊黃布企係隔黎人地就知咩事。大陸憤青最憎架仔，暴發戶又媚外，你d架妹同鬼妹碟勁好賣。d碟唔係跟身，搵條後巷收好，有人黎就帶佢去收貨，一隻賣佢100蚊，一路賣一收收錢之餘一路將你d假人仔唱番晒出去。<br />\n<br />\n賣完50隻，你應該已經賺到5000蚊，連埋你本身果47蚊+4蚊，已有5052蚊，你既利潤100%，冇野好搵得過咁。如是這你重複50，你既複利率收益已過億，可以買張武漢高鐵飛坐去溫州，用現金收購就黎執既廠，再請人造名牌手袋當真賣，不出3個月可翻10倍，到時應該有正牌注意到你，同你打官司，你就比5000萬個官庭外和解，跟住執左間廠，渣住9500萬番黎香港準備買殼股上市。<br />\n<br />\n上市後洗人去蒙古做假新聞，話你間野挖到地下有稀土，即時炒起隻股，3日內再賺10倍，然後配股比基金佬配到自己既股份唔夠5%，你就正式引退，求其捐1000萬比仁濟醫院拎個名人身份黎做，再洗100萬登7張報紙支持政改同起高鐵，等特區政府頒大紫荊比你。<br />\n<br />\n最後一步，就係等，等咩野？等天災。你最後需要既係一個機會，一有大型天災係內地發生，你捐會副身家上去，然後係街執垃圾比香港傳媒影到，舉世讚美你，1年內就做人大。<br />\n<br />\n做人大後你有得選舉共產黨既常委，選自己，呢個時候唔好忘記你當初留低既47蚊+4蚊，去搵萬里，佢係中共前朝唯一未死既大佬，你拎呢52蚊出黎話係你全副身家，佢會深受感動，重拾共產黨當年起義既激情，結果拉人隊幫拖投你，以佢既影響你你足到被委任為黨主席，去到呢步，自然就買到層樓㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7f8bd9522bde55aceea020041539c9d4f9b77b8","tid":518164,"uid":44267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T06:32:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://shop.r10s.jp/e-bloomstore/cabinet/nano/pn-101.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshop.r10s.jp%2Fe-bloomstore%2Fcabinet%2Fnano%2Fpn-101.jpg&h=36d70f55&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11ca5c51b80e5805f19d181b1bebf29bea417688","tid":518164,"uid":7306,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T06:43:47.000Z","msg":"香港女人真係唔撚知醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d39b0d0e32e012370233edc68c116a22f7cda940","tid":518164,"uid":44237,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T06:44:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/03/144219_85eb8f987b40153647bcea60a6879989.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F03%2F144219_85eb8f987b40153647bcea60a6879989.png&h=eb58fbc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n⼃<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/03/144223_76b2022bd500475673a134f3ee63e781.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F03%2F144223_76b2022bd500475673a134f3ee63e781.png&h=1a2bee7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我阿妹聖誕都整左個比佢條仔<br />\n不過都要整成個月<br />\n你到時咪氹下佢話大屋就未買到<br />\n睇住個小屋 幻想下你地嘅將來<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe474a2efd84cb32e9dabaf5e76e1add9eea0fae","tid":518164,"uid":28256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79f86520aba69aed04f81670c6e06bdecbc455f7","tid":518164,"uid":134834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad163ff8724bb49b9ee423359de1d40eff6a1dd1","tid":518164,"uid":105624,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T05:45:58.000Z","msg":"拿，是但去十二蚊店買碌棍，大大力扑落佢個頭到，就會有層樓架啦。如果仲咁貪心嫌少，扑多下送多層比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T06:24:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T06:45:17.000Z","msg":"愈大力樓底愈高<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打到夠掛座水晶燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"888cf869610967d5f5fa3f6b312667de034acf72","tid":518164,"uid":153412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c1fa2ef35ca9dc74eea17df26857002a6690446","tid":518164,"uid":19592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T04:47:40.000Z","msg":"如何有創意地，<br />\n喺100蚊內搞下笑完成哩個要求。<br />\n<br />\n最好唔好搞到分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T06:52:31.000Z","msg":"買間蟑螂屋比巨～<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"999fc34afd4fb9ddda1dcae3bd1c0b746e09fb8c","tid":518164,"uid":54226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T06:53:39.000Z","msg":"咁多位巴打好風趣幽默<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0785cbdec94e144b9bd3fe2d4f9b67ba356c5b6b","tid":518164,"uid":60287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T07:02:20.000Z","msg":"係條J度畫幾個窗口露台，然後今晚訓係床上面比個surprise佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 前提你要夠長"},{"pid":"6045a2dd1c0689e5efdce3116bf3a03c85f02436","tid":518164,"uid":69168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T07:04:12.000Z","msg":"買盒大富翁咪得囉，<br />\n要清水灣又得，要監獄都得呀"},{"pid":"f838974fc487245b96c3a1aa281e2beb2da83219","tid":518164,"uid":75373,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T07:08:51.000Z","msg":"聖誕節係淘寶淘左番黎 &yen;85人仔 見你咁慘 原價讓俾你先啦唉 我再買過<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/03/150658_19e6f6807dcfc1634ad87bc5c85b64c7.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F03%2F150658_19e6f6807dcfc1634ad87bc5c85b64c7.jpeg&h=947120b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb30222bb50a315e891b2c97ffea4b96f48c3ddd","tid":518164,"uid":151534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f838974fc487245b96c3a1aa281e2beb2da83219","tid":518164,"uid":75373,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T07:08:51.000Z","msg":"聖誕節係淘寶淘左番黎 &yen;85人仔 見你咁慘 原價讓俾你先啦唉 我再買過<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/03/150658_19e6f6807dcfc1634ad87bc5c85b64c7.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F03%2F150658_19e6f6807dcfc1634ad87bc5c85b64c7.jpeg&h=947120b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T07:10:28.000Z","msg":"屌你真係有<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"844623a282cabbb972134e568c04e8192416cfea","tid":518164,"uid":134834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T07:11:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一百蚊就唔得喇 四五千都有得搞搞佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你先去買兩張廣州直通車飛，就400蚊，再去信和買1000蚊咸碟，同佢講大量買打個折，應該買到50隻以上，要買鬼妹同日本妹的，唔好買其他，理由下面再講。<br />\n<br />\n坐到上廣州你手上仲有100蚊，去買包雲煙5蚊，然後係車站旁邊睇下邊個蛇頭鼠眼，打個眼色比佢佢就知你想唱假人仔，90蚊唱500蚊番黎，同佢講要唱散唔要100蚊紙。唱完拎包煙出黎問佢食唔食，佢見你幫襯佢就有計傾，你打蛇隨棍上問下邊到賣咸碟好。<br />\n<br />\n將淨低果5蚊打散，用1蚊搭巴士入城，搵佢講既地方。然後搵間士多買罐可樂，比唱番黎既假50蚊佢，找番47蚊真人仔，袋好準備最後用。<br />\n<br />\n等到日落你就開始擺地攤，乜都唔洗，只要擺一塊黃布企係隔黎人地就知咩事。大陸憤青最憎架仔，暴發戶又媚外，你d架妹同鬼妹碟勁好賣。d碟唔係跟身，搵條後巷收好，有人黎就帶佢去收貨，一隻賣佢100蚊，一路賣一收收錢之餘一路將你d假人仔唱番晒出去。<br />\n<br />\n賣完50隻，你應該已經賺到5000蚊，連埋你本身果47蚊+4蚊，已有5052蚊，你既利潤100%，冇野好搵得過咁。如是這你重複50，你既複利率收益已過億，可以買張武漢高鐵飛坐去溫州，用現金收購就黎執既廠，再請人造名牌手袋當真賣，不出3個月可翻10倍，到時應該有正牌注意到你，同你打官司，你就比5000萬個官庭外和解，跟住執左間廠，渣住9500萬番黎香港準備買殼股上市。<br />\n<br />\n上市後洗人去蒙古做假新聞，話你間野挖到地下有稀土，即時炒起隻股，3日內再賺10倍，然後配股比基金佬配到自己既股份唔夠5%，你就正式引退，求其捐1000萬比仁濟醫院拎個名人身份黎做，再洗100萬登7張報紙支持政改同起高鐵，等特區政府頒大紫荊比你。<br />\n<br />\n最後一步，就係等，等咩野？等天災。你最後需要既係一個機會，一有大型天災係內地發生，你捐會副身家上去，然後係街執垃圾比香港傳媒影到，舉世讚美你，1年內就做人大。<br />\n<br />\n做人大後你有得選舉共產黨既常委，選自己，呢個時候唔好忘記你當初留低既47蚊+4蚊，去搵<span style=\"color: red;\">萬里</span>，佢係中共前朝唯一未死既大佬，你拎呢52蚊出黎話係你全副身家，佢會深受感動，重拾共產黨當年起義既激情，結果拉人隊幫拖投你，以佢既影響你你足到被委任為黨主席，去到呢步，自然就買到層樓㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n2015年7月15日下午，澎湃新聞引述萬里之子萬伯翱消息表示萬里已於當天中午12點55分因病在北京逝世。不同尋常的是，這是由非官方主流媒體率先披露的前高層領導人死訊。此後，香港《蘋果日報》、上海《東方早報》、網易等媒體也先後作了相關報導。[8][9]<br />\n<br />\n晚間7時，中國官媒中央電視台在《新聞聯播》中以長達10分50秒的新聞片播報了中共中央、全國人大、國務院及全國政協四套班子發布的萬里逝世訃告，訃告中評價萬里為「中國共產黨的優秀黨員，久經考驗的忠誠的共產主義戰士，傑出的無產階級革命家、政治家，黨和國家的卓越領導人」。更以2285字的篇幅全面地敘述了萬里的生平。文末更對萬里做出了極高評價，稱萬里「一生堅持真理，堅持正義，堅持原則，顧全大局，遵守黨的紀律，維護黨的團結，對改進作風、堅決懲治腐敗堅定支持」。[10]<br />\n<br />\n晚間8時許，官方的新華社也全文播發了四套班子的萬里逝世訃告。"},{"pid":"63ee942b8d7043801f6b02d01fa4f26a25835cf4","tid":518164,"uid":62650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T07:31:41.000Z","msg":"monopoly"},{"pid":"e6a87fb0d664272853c91121a878f473a311f32a","tid":518164,"uid":11055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:47:18.000Z","msg":"萬里15年個陣死撚左口廿<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01838a1cdde9bec050a2887dda9cb128a45cfcfc","tid":518164,"uid":150230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T09:10:06.000Z","msg":"中出佢即飛算啦"},{"pid":"ef9f6e73c30c1e3a4cddce970ae845571a5f6629","tid":518164,"uid":103531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T09:11:44.000Z","msg":"來來曱甴屋"},{"pid":"5fcc05a9dab3102b02a8b57f5fdd681a42044ef8","tid":518164,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T09:18:10.000Z","msg":"買條門匙比佢, 求其講個地址叫佢自己去開"}]}